Record of Phase 1 was carried forward to Liguilla de no descenso.
Initially bottom-4 relegated

(1) Aucas play playoff with Politécnico (Pichincha's second division 
    champion) to decide which team of Pichincha is relegated to second
    division; according to reglementation to 1971 Pichincha only can 
    have 4 teams in National Championship.
(2) LDU de Portoviejo maintained in National Championship 1971 by decision of
    Extraordinary Congress of Federación Ecuatoriana de Fútbol.

